SELECT 78, Total_Cattle FROM farm_competition LEFT JOIN competition_record LEFT JOIN city LEFT JOIN farm ON competition_record.Farm_ID = farm.Cows AND farm.Farm_ID = city.City_ID AND city.Official_Name = farm_competition.Hosts WHERE (Hosts NOT IN (orange, grape, banana, apple, pineapple)) OR ( farm_competition.Competition_ID > Population) GROUP BY Total_Cattle ORDER BY Total_Cattle ASC LIMIT 7
